    "Therefore, any configuration setting (such as temperature) that receives a larger share of overall production deployment trials is at a disadvantage compared to those that receive a smaller share.Finally, we report the results for the two different language models used in the test-a-thons, overall (Table 5) and per platform (Table 6).",
